Ng%C5%A9-B%C3%A0n/poem-GY5OMYn37RrHwtCXg78ABg">Ngũ Bàn - 五盤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-l%E1%BB%99/poem-P3ZVYDAknpQEyl0aTQKiQA">Thái Bình lộ - 太平路</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Kinh-Nam-t%E1%BB%91ng-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Th%E1%BB%A7-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-minh-ph%E1%BB%A7-t%E1%BB%AB-m%C3%A3n-c%C3%A1o-bi%E1%BB%87t-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-Bfz7q1pPB52k-USL3w8zKg">Thu nhật Kinh Nam tống Thạch Thủ Tiết minh phủ từ mãn cáo biệt, phụng ký Tiết thượng thư tụng đức tự hoài phỉ nhiên chi tác, tam thập vận - 秋日荊南送石首薛明府辭滿告別奉寄薛尚書頌德敘懷斐然之作三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C3%A0o-th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-kinh/poem-uMzfvpbR-GUIWYyFWbbyBg">Tiễn Đào thị độc thướng kinh - 餞陶侍讀上京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Y%E1%BA%BFt-V%C4%83n-c%C3%B4ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-wuXBuRo8o7HE9hqjf6JGGA">Yết Văn công thượng phương - 謁文公上方</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
